{"tid":1817534,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國國務卿: 中聯辦如希望香港“重回正軌”, 請遵守《中英聯合聲明》","createTime":"2020-01-09T07:23:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T00:04:08.000Z","uid":134071,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"eb5fb7e99129816241e57f5e3cd03c55aeed09b1","tid":1817534,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T07:23:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/6720398/article-新中聯辦主任盼港返正軌-美國務卿：中共履諾才是/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2F6720398%2Farticle-%E6%96%B0%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%BB%E7%9B%BC%E6%B8%AF%E8%BF%94%E6%AD%A3%E8%BB%8C-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%99%E5%8D%BF%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E5%B1%A5%E8%AB%BE%E6%89%8D%E6%98%AF%2F&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF06joMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=bd3e36e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/6720398/article-新中聯辦主任盼港返正軌-美國務卿：中共履諾才是/</a><br />\n<br />\n駱惠寧盼港重回正軌 龐培歐：北京履行承諾才是正軌<br />\n華盛頓記者張加／即時報導 2020年01月08日 06:06<br />\n<br />\n<strong>美國國務卿龐培歐7日談及香港情勢，指中聯辦新主任駱惠寧盼香港能重回正軌，美方認為「正軌」即是中共遵守中英聯合聲明，以及其對香港的承諾。</strong><br />\n<br />\n龐培歐7日在國務院舉行記者會，談及香港、北韓、伊朗等事務；龐培歐主動提到美方知道中方任命駱惠寧出任中聯辦主任，駱惠寧說期盼香港重回正軌。<br />\n<br />\n龐培歐表示，正軌就是美方之前所說，中共遵守對香港所做的承諾，遵守中英聯合聲明，保障其自由與法治。<br />\n<br />\n龐培歐指出，美方將繼續與香港和中方官員合作，以維護香港的人權、基本自由與高度自治。<br />\n<br />\n駱惠寧日前見媒體時表示，近半年來，香港的形勢讓人揪心，大家都熱切期盼香港能重回正軌；對香港來說，「一國兩制」是最大的優勢，今後中聯辦、林鄭政府，連同社會各界共同努力之下，一定能確保憲法、基本法在香港得到全面貫徹實施，確保「一國兩制」行穩致遠，讓香港長期繁榮穩定。"},{"pid":"4e8827e234828bab0f5d066c9d75f764fcba914a","tid":1817534,"uid":134071,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T07:23:38.000Z","msg":"美國正面還擊中聯辦！"},{"pid":"29e3d6a1bc80038049b3eb4fe849cce5f207bb64","tid":1817534,"uid":271857,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T07:24:44.000Z","msg":"支那點會明咩係合約精神。"},{"pid":"01aad88023acf31d3e100b23852a88e18660fb18","tid":1817534,"uid":120541,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T07:25:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">解放軍撤出香港，香港就可以重回正軌喇</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b56d263a21d886957cd311714fee9fe2f3916e53","tid":1817534,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T07:25:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"115d9c5dfb66ade971996a4a3c79903a85ba0bd4","tid":1817534,"uid":61197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T07:28:23.000Z","msg":"thanks you, sir!"},{"pid":"89b782c4457b67b58b69300618b532cc865c1cf5","tid":1817534,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T07:28:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4e1c7c162d8552c9d1a4dfc2203470a04865395","tid":1817534,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T07:30:34.000Z","msg":"可以停止叫英國廢聲明未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b9a57467155141b6954e3ae82fd145595777fd","tid":1817534,"uid":51057,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T07:31:52.000Z","msg":"歷史文件<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb2b971dbda8acc1ddfb408cb00d24c55da4e9a","tid":1817534,"uid":254594,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"01aad88023acf31d3e100b23852a88e18660fb18","tid":1817534,"uid":120541,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T07:25:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">解放軍撤出香港，香港就可以重回正軌喇</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T07:31:58.000Z","msg":"警犬唔洗？"},{"pid":"f8543c5aa3f73062be3bd8a62daf75d36710efa8","tid":1817534,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T07:31:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\